    {
      "id": "m1",
      "text": "What is the derivative of x^2?",
      "isFormula": false,
      "options": [
        { "id": "a", "text": "x", "isFormula": false },
        { "id": "b", "text": "2x", "isFormula": true },
        { "id": "c", "text": "x^3", "isFormula": true },
        { "id": "d", "text": "2", "isFormula": false }
      ],
      "correctOptionId": "b",
      "explanation": "Using the power rule, d/dx(x^n) = n·x^(n-1), so d/dx(x^2) = 2x."
    },
    {
